			<div id="breadcrumbs">You are here: <div id="breadcrumbs"><a href="index.php?sec=739">Home</a> </div></div><div class="content" id="content2144"><div class="headline" id="headline2144"><h1>HOME PAGE</h1></div><div class="body" id="body2144"><p align="center">&nbsp;</p>
<p align="center"><strong><em><font size="3">The Society for Accessible Travel &amp; Hospitality (SATH), founded in 1976, is an educational nonprofit membership organization whose mission is to raise awareness of the needs of all travelers with disabilities, remove physical and attitudinal barriers to free access and expand travel opportunities in the United States and abroad. Members include travel professionals, consumers with disabilities and other individuals and corporations who support our mission. </font></em></strong></p>
<p style="margin-right: -0.5in;" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<h1 style="margin-top: 12pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: center; "><span lang="EN-CA"><img src="/images/image/IMG-1.jpg" alt="" style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 13px; width: 593px; height: 482px; " /></span></h1>
<h1 style="margin: 12pt 0in 3pt; text-align: center;">&nbsp;We are proud to be</h1>
<h1 style="margin: 12pt 0in 3pt; text-align: center;">An&nbsp;Organizational Sponsor Of Abitlties Expo</h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.abilitiesexpo.com/"><input type="image" src="/images/image/Abilities Expo.jpg" width="199" height="71" /></a></p>
<h1 style="margin-top: 12pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: center; "><span lang="EN-CA"><font size="5"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><a href="http://sath.org/page/OUR_HOLIDAY_GIFT_TO_OUR_MEMBERS/10596/812/">A Home Exchange V</a></span></font></span><a href="http://sath.org/page/OUR_HOLIDAY_GIFT_TO_OUR_MEMBERS/10596/812/" style="font-size: x-large; "><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">acation&mdash;Our Gift to You</span></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;</h1>
